<h1>Form Controls</h1>

<p>The form control component is used as a container for a form input, label, validation & other common form UI.</p>

<h2>Basic Usage</h2>

<p>Let's look at a basic example:</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="form-control"}}
    {{#uxs-form-control}}
      <div>Form Control content.</div>
    {{/uxs-form-control}}
  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet 'form-control.hbs'}}

{{/docs-demo}}


<h2>Common Usage</h2>

<p>Let's look at a common example where we define the controls child element through properties:</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="form-control-properties"}}
    {{uxs-form-control
      label=label
      disabled=disabled
      type=type
      value=value
      name="my-control"
      tip=tip
      warning=warning
      error=error
    }}
  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet 'form-control-properties.hbs'}}

{{/docs-demo}}

