<h2>Custom Usage</h2>

<p>Although the above should cover 90% of your common use cases, we can customise the control with contextual components:</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="form-control-custom"}}
    {{#uxs-form-control as |control|}}
      {{control.label "Username" disabled=disabled}}
      {{control.input value="Foo"}}
      {{control.tip "Think of a unique usename. This will be publicly visible."}}
    {{/uxs-form-control}}
  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet 'form-control-custom.hbs'}}

{{/docs-demo}}
